<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/defence-infrastructure-organisation/about> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Defence Infrastructure Organisation (DIO) is the estate expert for defence, supporting the armed forces to enable military capability by planning, building, maintaining, and servicing infrastructure."@en .
